r />\n之後個汁次次都煮到一pat pat咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求連登各廚神指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記住煮既時候落橄欖油、重要落鹽同胡椒粉。煮到咁上下記住要邊試熟度 同邊煮 時間好難掌握既話 其實一般意粉大概5-7分鐘就咩都熟架嗱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n包裝紙有寫大約要煮幾多分鐘 差唔多夠鐘前1-2分鐘可以撈一條摸下/試下軟硬度 到你覺得可以就上碟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad2f6b538eba3d2adcaa48e2e0f345ce9535380","tid":174684,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"落紅糖"},{"pid":"b558c2d7a61b4b7319d99a5eae07f4e4862c234e","tid":174684,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"用新鮮番茄做汁, 已經夠屌打九成香港D街上市賣既意粉.<br />\n<br />\n總之用新鮮材料係無得輸, D沖既濃淡厚簿就個人口味."},{"pid":"db282b8a03589a237096cba68214d5afe8c9e57e","tid":174684,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T04:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次都煮到好似狗飯咁，同出面個啲差十條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後個汁次次都煮到一pat pat咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求連登各廚神指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記住<span style=\"color: blue;\">煮既時候落橄欖油</span>、重要落鹽同<span style=\"color: blue;\">胡椒粉</span>。煮到咁上下記住要邊試熟度 同邊煮 時間好難掌握既話 其實一般意粉大概5-7分鐘就咩都熟架嗱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n意大利人唔會落<br />\n時間視乎粗幼而定</blockquote><br />\n我自己煮開扁意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99238b1241172fbad5f778bcf9a3c686c4de466","tid":174684,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次都煮到好似狗飯咁，同出面個啲差十條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後個汁次次都煮到一pat pat咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求連登各廚神指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記住<span style=\"color: blue;\">煮既時候落橄欖油</span>、重要落鹽同<span style=\"color: blue;\">胡椒粉</span>。煮到咁上下記住要邊試熟度 同邊煮 時間好難掌握既話 其實一般意粉大概5-7分鐘就咩都熟架嗱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n意大利人唔會落<br />\n時間視乎粗幼而定</blockquote><br />\n我自己煮開扁意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n扁通常煮耐少少<br />\n正路如果你係整茄醬呢啲<br />\n你跟包裝建議嘅時間最細果個時間<br />\n夠鐘就去水再撈落茄醬燘多一分鐘<br />\n<br />\n不過你如果怕淋，最好買新鮮軟身，會襟啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ed5db52abd7b637f67bc830c16bedbc723c96f","tid":174684,"uid":38923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次都煮到好似狗飯咁，同出面個啲差十條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後個汁次次都煮到一pat pat咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求連登各廚神指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記住<span style=\"color: blue;\">煮既時候落橄欖油</span>、重要落鹽同<span style=\"color: blue;\">胡椒粉</span>。煮到咁上下記住要邊試熟度 同邊煮 時間好難掌握既話 其實一般意粉大概5-7分鐘就咩都熟架嗱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n意大利人唔會落<br />\n時間視乎粗幼而定</blockquote><br />\n我自己煮開扁意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n扁通常煮耐少少<br />\n正路如果你係整茄醬呢啲<br />\n你跟包裝建議嘅時間最細果個時間<br />\n夠鐘就去水再撈落茄醬燘多一分鐘<br />\n<br />\n不過你如果怕淋，最好買新鮮軟身，會襟啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解煮扁意好易痴埋一齊<br />\nspaghetti就唔會<br />\n仲有如果落汁就唔好加油煮意粉"},{"pid":"f365a907034b60faa8cde9c7ffcfaf1e7cb4132e","tid":174684,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次都煮到好似狗飯咁，同出面個啲差十條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後個汁次次都煮到一pat pat咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求連登各廚神指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記住<span style=\"color: blue;\">煮既時候落橄欖油</span>、重要落鹽同<span style=\"color: blue;\">胡椒粉</span>。煮到咁上下記住要邊試熟度 同邊煮 時間好難掌握既話 其實一般意粉大概5-7分鐘就咩都熟架嗱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n意大利人唔會落<br />\n時間視乎粗幼而定</blockquote><br />\n我自己煮開扁意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n扁通常煮耐少少<br />\n正路如果你係整茄醬呢啲<br />\n你跟包裝建議嘅時間最細果個時間<br />\n夠鐘就去水再撈落茄醬燘多一分鐘<br />\n<br />\n不過你如果怕淋，最好買新鮮軟身，會襟啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解煮扁意好易痴埋一齊<br />\nspaghetti就唔會<br />\n仲有如果落汁就唔好加油煮意粉</blockquote><br />\n煮果時可以了下佢<br />\n唔得嘅話可能係隻意粉問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758605bb3adacb34ac06d7a5470fcce940185aaa","tid":174684,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"聽日講要過冷河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係會有鹼水味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f02501100e4ece58f179384600523cd06f69d3","tid":174684,"uid":38923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次都煮到好似狗飯咁，同出面個啲差十條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後個汁次次都煮到一pat pat咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求連登各廚神指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no